title: Debbie Does Dallas: The Musical
overview: The rags-to-riches story of small-town all-American sweetheart Debbie Benton working to become a Texas Cowgirl Cheerleader. To afford the bus fare standing between her and that dream, she and her friends start Teen Services but it doesn't pay enough. They find their enthusiasm back when they realize they can get more money by being "good girls" and performing "little favors".
